1) Create new ELB volume from the console and attach to running ec2 instance
2) Login to server and create new fs
3) lslbk  ==> to check the if newly created volume is available
4) mkfs.ext4 /dev/xvdf ==> to crate new file system of ext4
5) mkdir data ==> to create a directory
6)mount /dev/xvdf data ==> to moun the fs with directory
7)Finally check the df -h
8)Also need to udpate in /etc/fstab
